Enum Class SVGUnit

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<SVGUnit>
org.tquadrat.foundation.svg.type.SVGUnit
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<SVGUnit>, Constable
@ClassVersion(sourceVersion="$Id: SVGUnit.java 1074 2023-10-02 12:05:06Z tquadrat $") @API(status=STABLE, since="0.0.5") public enum SVGUnit extends Enum<SVGUnit>
SVG allows different units for some attributes; this class defines these units and the transformations into Strings for those units.
Author:
Thomas Thrien (thomas.thrien@tquadrat.org)
Version:
$Id: SVGUnit.java 1074 2023-10-02 12:05:06Z tquadrat $
